Third-party components
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sandbox base image and packages
  The sandbox image is built on Chainguard's Wolfi base image
  (cgr.dev/chainguard/wolfi-base) and installs packages from the Wolfi OS
  repository (https://github.com/wolfi-dev/os). Each package is used under its
  own open-source license; `sluice lock` and `sluice lock --sbom` inventory what
  is installed on top of the base. sluice is an independent project and is not
  affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed by Chainguard.

Test framework
  The test suite uses bats-core (https://github.com/bats-core/bats-core) and its
  helper libraries bats-support, bats-assert, and bats-file, vendored as git
  submodules under test/.
